London - She is already an accomplished scene-stealer - so it’s no surprise that Princess Charlotte is at the centre of all the fun in Princess Eugenie’s first social media post since her wedding.
The three-year-old is shown laughing as she gazes up at the new Mrs Brooksbank, surrounded by bridesmaids and pageboys. 

Eugenie is sitting on the floor of Windsor Castle’s White Drawing Room with husband Jack (beside Theodora Williams), while Savannah Phillips wraps her arms around the bride. 
