Isla Phillips can also be seen at the front. Posting on Instagram, Eugenie, 28, wrote: "Jack and I would like to thank everyone who was involved in making our day so special and for all the wonderful wishes as we start married life laughing together."
The informal picture was taken by wedding photographer Alex Bramall on Friday.
Another scene stealer was Teddy Williams. The six-year-old daughter of Robbie Williams and Ayda Field, who is seldom pictured in public, made her royal debut as bridesmaid. AdChoicesADVERTISINGinRead invented by Teads

The splitting image of her dad, young Teddy had a cheeky moment when she asked Sarah Ferguson if she was the Queen.
